  <brief_title>Treatment of Withdrawal Symptoms With NADA Acupuncture in Chronic Pain Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of NADA Acupuncture for Treatment of Withdrawal Symptoms During Gradual Opioid Withdrawal in Chronic Pain Patients</official_title>
